&lt;h5&gt;Growe welcomes those who are excited to:&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Conduct ad hoc and ongoing KYB checks and monitoring of contractual companies and accompany the due diligence process of signing contracts;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work collaboratively with other members of the Compliance team, frontline staff and managers to identify opportunities for improving compliance across the company and support their implementation where appropriate;&lt;/p&gt;
