&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent knowledge of MS Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint);&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of legal requirements and controls (e.g. 4th or 5th Anti-Money Laundering Directive, FATF recommendations, MIFID II);&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fluent oral and written communication skills in English;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Professional certification (e.g. CySEC Basic or Advanced) is a plus;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Legal background in gambling will be considered an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;We appreciate if you have those personal features:&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to think outside the box;&lt;/p&gt;
