&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Practical experience with Infrastructure as Code tools such as Terraform, Helm, or Ansible;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience integrating security logs and events with SIEM platforms and supporting detection, monitoring, and incident response use cases;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to balance security requirements with business objectives and engineering velocity;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Python will be a plus;&lt;/li&gt;
